=Description=

"Openbravo is the award-winning developer of Openbravo ERP, a web-based commercial open source ERP solution for SMBs-- the industry's first real alternative to proprietary software. The company's Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) and Point of Sale (PoS) solutions, the most popular in their market, have been downloaded more than 1.5 million times and are used in over 50 countries." ~(http://www.openbravo.com/about-us/)

=P2P Perspectives=

Openbravo covers a great deal of ground for a small or medium sized business.  For a small shop that wants to be part of a P2P network Openbravo can be a point of standardization with other businesses in the network.



